    "0.1 - System Overview": {
        "level": 1,
        "html": "<!-- header 2 -->\r\n<h2>0.1 - System Overview</h2>\r\n\r\n<!-- paragraph -->\r\n<p>\r\n\tThis system is made to automate the customer management and sales process for Hairliners Salon, enhancing efficiency and improving customer service.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> The system consists of various integrated modules to help fulfill its intended purpose. Here are the modules available in the system: \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<!-- Ordered List (1., 2., ...)-->\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<!-- list item -->\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<b>Login Module</b> -  Login Module ensures safe access and user accountability.\r\n\t</li>\r\n    <!-- centered image -->\r\n<center><img src=\"images/login.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The login screen</i></center>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<b>Customer Management</b> - The Customer Management Module displays list of customers as well as enables registration of new customers and quick information retrieval.\r\n\t</li>\r\n<center><img src=\"images/customermanagement.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The customer management screen</i></center>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<b>Point of Sales</b> -  Point of Sales Module facilitates list of sales record and facilitates record creation. \r\n\t</li>\r\n<center><img src=\"images/pointofsales.png\"></img></center>\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The point of sales screen</i></center>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <b>Inventory</b> -  Inventory Module displays list of stock as well as managing stock updates and usage tracking.  \r\n    </li>\r\n<center><img src=\"images/inventory.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The inventory screen</i></center>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<b>User Management (Admin Only)</b> -  User Management Module displays staff members and user type, it also monitors user actions/activity. \r\n\t</li>\r\n <center><img src=\"images/usermanagement.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The user management screen</i></center>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <b>Report (Admin Only)</b> -  Report Module generates comprehensive reports on customers, sales, inventory, and user activities.  \r\n    </li>\r\n<center><img src=\"images/report.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The report screen</i></center>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <b>Maintenance (Admin Only)</b> -  Maintenance Module allows to backup and restore data.  \r\n    </li>\r\n<center><img src=\"images/maintenance.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The maintenance screen</i></center>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <b>Help</b> -  Help Module generates provides a User Manual and FAQ  \r\n    </li>\r\n<center><img src=\"images/helpscreen.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The help screen</i></center>\r\n    <li>\r\n        <b>About</b> -  About Module offers software and developers information.  \r\n    </li>\r\n<center><img src=\"images/about.png\"></img></center>\r\n\r\n<!-- centered and italic -->\r\n<center><i>The about screen</i></center>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n"
    },
    "0.2 - Software and Hardware": {
        "level": 1,
        "html": "<!-- header 2 -->\r\n<h2>0.2 - Software and Hardware Requirements</h2>\r\n\r\n<!-- paragraph -->\r\n<p>\r\n\tThe system requires specific hardware and software to ensure optimal performance for staff and admin users. \r\n</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<!-- list item -->\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<b>Hardware</b> - These are the minimum hardware requirements: a processor equivalent to at least an Intel Core i3, at least 4 GB of RAM, and a minimum of 128 GB SSD storage. Additional peripherals include a monitor with a resolution of 1920x1080 or higher, a keyboard, a mouse, and backup storage like an external hard drive or network-attached storage.\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<b>Software</b> - Here is the corrected version of your text:\r\n\r\n\t\t---\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\tFor software, it should have at least Windows 10 or later as the operating system and must use the latest version of Chrome, Firefox, or Edge browsers. Additional necessary software includes backup software for regular database and application data backups, security software such as antivirus and firewall, and a PDF reader for documentation and reports.\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t</ol>\r\n<p>  These requirements ensure smooth and efficient system operation for all users.\r\n</p>\r\n"
    },
